&lt;p>Hameldon, (Trig Point at SX 70313 80573, elevation 529 metres / 1735 feet) across the East Webburn River.&lt;/p>
&lt;p>The East Webburn rises near Grimspound and flows through Widecombe to join the West Webburn River south of Widecombe at Lizwell Meet (Oakmoor Wood), at SX 71335 73703.&lt;/p>
